<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><i style=""><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">(Use for those who notified us)<br></font></i><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Thank you for your time today and for notifying us that you would like to make a potential Professional Indemnity claim.<br></span><i style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>(Use for those where we received notification)<br></i><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">We have received notification of a potential claim being made against you for (insert allegations and claimant here).<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>So that we can present a claim to our insurers, please may you kindly forward the following:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"></p><ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Overview of events to date giving as much detail as possible</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The dates of when the incident occurred</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">When the intimated potential claim was made against you if this is the case</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">An idea if you can of a possible reserve against the claim – attaching figures if any figures have been disclosed</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Claimant’s name, address, and contact details</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Statement from the Client or as much detail as you can with attachments</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Copies of prior correspondence, email or any other correspondence received</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Confirmation of contractor(s) and full name(s) if applicable</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Explain if you know, their view of responsibility</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">As much information on the records / paperwork that you have kept as support</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Confirmation of your VAT status</font></li></ul><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">I attached a copy of your policy schedule and wording to assist.<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Once I have received all your information, I can present the details to our insurers. Depending on how quickly you are able to return the information back to me will determine the timeframe for this.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Once this has been passed to insurers, the insurers may be in contact directly with you. However we are here to support at any time.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Claims Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: claims@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>